## 7. Common Framework Span Attributes

All framework spans (agent, workflow, tool) MUST set these attributes:

```typescript
span.setAttribute('telemetry.sdk.name', 'openlit');
span.setAttribute('deployment.environment', OpenlitConfig.environment);
span.setAttribute('service.name', OpenlitConfig.applicationName);
span.setAttribute('gen_ai.sdk.version', SDK_VERSION);
span.setAttribute('gen_ai.operation.name', operationName);
span.setAttribute('gen_ai.provider.name', frameworkSystem);
```

Plus `applyCustomSpanAttributes(span)` MUST be called on EVERY framework span (not just LLM spans).

