| Framework | JS Package | Python Reference | Mechanism | Built-in Telemetry | Key Pattern |
|-----------|-----------|-----------------|-----------|-------------------|-------------|
| LangChain | `@langchain/core` | `sdk/python/src/openlit/instrumentation/langchain/` | Callback injection | LangSmith (not OTel) | Inject handler via `_configureSync` |
| LangGraph | `@langchain/langgraph` | `sdk/python/src/openlit/instrumentation/langgraph/` | Monkey-patch | LangSmith (not OTel) | Wrap `Pregel.invoke/stream`, `StateGraph.compile/add_node` |
| OpenAI Agents | `@openai/agents` | `sdk/python/src/openlit/instrumentation/openai_agents/` | TracingProcessor | Custom (not OTel) | Register via `addTraceProcessor()`, skip `response`/`generation` |
| Mastra | `@mastra/core` | N/A (JS only) | SpanProcessor | Yes (native OTel) | Enrich/normalize Mastra spans |
| Claude Agents SDK | `@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk` | `sdk/python/src/openlit/instrumentation/claude_agent_sdk/` | Monkey-patch + hooks | No | Wrap `query()`, client methods |
| Google ADK | `@google/adk` | `sdk/python/src/openlit/instrumentation/google_adk/` | Monkey-patch + PassthroughTracer | Cloud Trace (OTel) | Replace ADK tracers, enrich LLM/tool spans |
| Strands Agents | `@strands-agents/sdk` | `sdk/python/src/openlit/instrumentation/strands/` | SpanProcessor | Yes (native OTel) | Detect by scope `strands.telemetry.tracer` |
| LlamaIndex | `llamaindex` | `sdk/python/src/openlit/instrumentation/llamaindex/` | Monkey-patch | Yes (workflow-otel) | Wrap engines, LLM, agent classes |

